---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Case Study: Kristina - Web Design Carmagnola | Bitora"
  description="Scopri come abbiamo trasformato la sartoria di Kristina con un sito web professionale e tessere NFC, aumentando le prenotazioni del 180% a Carmagnola."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero del progetto -->
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-800 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
              Case Study
            </span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              Kristina
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Come abbiamo trasformato una sartoria tradizionale di Carmagnola in un business digitale moderno
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Showcase del progetto -->
          <div class="relative">
            <!-- Logo/Brand Section -->
            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                  <span class="text-white text-2xl font-bold">K</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left">
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Kristina</h3>
                  <p class="text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 font-medium">Sartoria d'Arte</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Carmagnola, TO</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Screenshot mockup -->
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-700 dark:to-gray-800 p-4">
              <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-xl shadow-inner overflow-hidden">
                <img 
                  src="/sartoria_kristina.png" 
                  alt="Sito web Kristina - Web Design Carmagnola"
                  class="w-full h-auto"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview del progetto -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <!-- Dettagli progetto -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">La sfida</h2>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
                Kristina gestiva una sartoria tradizionale a Carmagnola, specializzata in abiti su misura e riparazioni sartoriali. 
                Pur avendo clienti fedeli, aveva difficoltà a mostrare i suoi lavori e ad attrarre nuovi clienti. 
                Il passaparola era il suo unico strumento di marketing, limitando fortemente la crescita del business.
              </p>
              
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">La soluzione</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
                Abbiamo creato un portfolio digitale elegante che racconta la storia e l'artigianalità di Kristina, 
                integrato con tessere NFC smart per il networking professionale e un sistema di prenotazione appuntamenti.
              </p>
              
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-purple-900 dark:text-purple-300">Prima</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                    <li>• Portfolio solo fisico</li>
                    <li>• Difficoltà a mostrare i lavori</li>
                    <li>• Solo passaparola</li>
                    <li>• Prenotazioni solo telefoniche</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 p-6 rounded-xl">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-green-900 dark:text-green-300">Dopo</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                    <li>• Portfolio digitale professionale</li>
                    <li>• Galleria lavori sempre aggiornata</li>
                    <li>• Biglietti NFC smart</li>
                    <li>• Prenotazioni online automatiche</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Sidebar info -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Dettagli Progetto</h3>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Cliente:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Kristina</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Settore:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Sartoria</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Località:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Carmagnola (TO)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Timeline:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2 settimane</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Anno:</span>
                    <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">2024</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 p-6 rounded-xl">
                <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-purple-900 dark:text-purple-300">Tecnologie Utilizzate</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-800 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-xs">Portfolio Gallery</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-800 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-xs">NFC Cards</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-800 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-xs">Booking System</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-800 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 rounded-full text-xs">Responsive Design</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Risultati -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 dark:from-purple-900/20 dark:to-pink-900/20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Risultati ottenuti</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
              In soli 3 mesi dal lancio, Kristina ha trasformato completamente il suo approccio al business
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">+5</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Nuovi clienti/settimana</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">75%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Conversione da portfolio</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">+85%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Visibilità social</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">4.7★</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Soddisfazione clienti</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonial -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6">"</div>
            <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed">
              Il biglietto NFC professionale mi ha permesso di distinguermi completamente. 
              Ora i clienti accedono al mio portfolio istantaneamente e posso mostrare tutti i miei lavori. 
              È stato un investimento che si è ripagato immediatamente.
            </blockquote>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">K</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-left">
                <div class="font-semibold text-lg">Kristina</div>
                <div class="opacity-90">Titolare, Kristina - Sartoria</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA finale -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-orange-600 text-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
            Pronto a trasformare il tuo business?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95">
            Come Kristina, anche tu puoi digitalizzare la tua attività e attrarre nuovi clienti
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="/contattaci" 
              class="bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors shadow-lg"
            >
              Inizia il tuo progetto
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/portfolio" 
              class="border-2 border-white/60 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white transition-colors"
            >
              Vedi altri progetti
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 text-sm opacity-80">
            ✅ Risultati misurabili
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>